This project involves the use of Sentiment Analysis, Predictive Analysis, Visualization and Comparison Module.
Dataset Link: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/nelgiriyewithana/world-stock-prices-daily-updating?resource=download
Results are mentioned below.

The predictive model shows that the estimate for the next three days is 229.4,229.8 and 230.2 according to the dataset. Forecasting was used to obtain this result on tableau.
Sentiment Analysis was done for Adidas using comparison between 50-day Moving Average and 200-day Moving Average. The 50-day MA generally crosses above the 200-day MA hence the stock sentiment shows potential upwars trend in the market.
Since, the dataset used is vast, comparison of multiple companies have been shown for various industries.

